query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `ai_training` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `activePersonaTemplate` varchar(50),
  `humorLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `friendlinessLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `formalityLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `enthusiasmLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `patienceLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `empathyLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `responseLength` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `responseDepth` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `exampleUsage` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `dataUsage` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `metaphorUsage` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `structuredResponse` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `proactiveness` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `questioningStyle` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `suggestionFrequency` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `humilityLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `persistenceLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `careLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `pushIntensity` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `urgencyCreation` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `priceSensitivity` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `comparisonUsage` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `closingIntensity` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `followUpFrequency` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `terminologyUsage` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `regulationAwareness` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `riskWarningLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `caseStudyUsage` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `marketAnalysis` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `educationalContent` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `soothingAbility` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `praiseFrequency` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `encouragementLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `negativeHandling` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `optimismLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `humorInTension` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `emojiUsage` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `colloquialLevel` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `cantoneseUsage` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `englishMixing` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `exclamationUsage` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `addressingStyle` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `topicRange` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `privacyAwareness` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `promiseCaution` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `referralWillingness` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `uncertaintyHandling` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `complaintHandling` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 3,
  `behaviorInstructions` text,
  `prohibitedActions` text,
  `customGreeting` text,
  `customClosing` text,
  `customPhrases` text,
  `trainingProgress` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `intelligenceScore` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 50,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `ai_training_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  CONSTRAINT `ai_training_userId_unique` UNIQUE(`userId`)
)
